Read Aloud is a famous Text-To-Speech browser extension with 65,065 Users &amp; Recommended badge on Firefox[1] and 3,000,000+ users on Chrome web store[2].<p>I saw a hyperlink with the text &#x27;India success [story]&#x27; on the footer of the popup of the extension. Clicking the URL leaded to the YouTube video titled &#x27;Home ivermectin based kits in India&#x27;[3].<p>Checking the code[4] the content for the hyperlink is fetched dynamically from the readaloud website[5].<p>```
{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ivermectin&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;India success [story]&quot;,&quot;link&quot;:&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;youtu.be&#x2F;eO9cjy3Rydc&quot;,&quot;period&quot;:1440}
```<p>The publisher of the extensions seems to be same as the developer, I have asked for clarifications on their GitHub issues[6].<p>[1] https:&#x2F;&#x2F;addons.mozilla.org&#x2F;en-US&#x2F;firefox&#x2F;addon&#x2F;read-aloud&#x2F;<p>[2] https:&#x2F;&#x2F;chrome.google.com&#x2F;webstore&#x2F;detail&#x2F;read-aloud-a-text-to-spee&#x2F;hdhinadidafjejdhmfkjgnolgimiaplp<p>[3] https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.youtube.com&#x2F;watch?v=eO9cjy3Rydc | https:&#x2F;&#x2F;web.archive.org&#x2F;web&#x2F;20210923144909&#x2F;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.youtube.com&#x2F;watch?v=eO9cjy3Rydc<p>[4] https:&#x2F;&#x2F;web.archive.org&#x2F;web&#x2F;20210923143226&#x2F;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;ken107&#x2F;read-aloud&#x2F;blob&#x2F;8770c74f323392ba113f50eb1c4014d07b28ffd9&#x2F;js&#x2F;popup.js<p>[5] https:&#x2F;&#x2F;support.readaloud.app&#x2F;read-aloud&#x2F;announcement | https:&#x2F;&#x2F;archive.is&#x2F;QUgkl<p>[6] https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;ken107&#x2F;read-aloud&#x2F;issues&#x2F;232 | https:&#x2F;&#x2F;web.archive.org&#x2F;web&#x2F;20210923150526&#x2F;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;ken107&#x2F;read-aloud&#x2F;issues&#x2F;232
